This directory contains Java source files for the Regalia Android application.

License classification by file:
  - StockfishNative.java: GPL v3 (derived from DroidFish)
      Engine management logic from DroidFish (ExternalEngine.java,
      InternalStockFish.java, UCIEngineBase.java, EngineUtil.java,
      DroidComputerPlayer.java). Copyright (C) Peter Österlund.
      Modifications Copyright (C) 2026 Regalia.
  - MainActivity.java: AGPL v3 (original)
      WebView host, immersive mode, lifecycle, SAF file-picker routing.
  - ChessApp.java: AGPL v3 (original)
      Application class, crash protection, locale detection.
  - ChessWebViewClient.java: AGPL v3 (original)
      Page load handler, JS bridge registration.
  - EngineService.java: AGPL v3 (original)
      Foreground service that keeps the engine subprocess alive on
      Android 14/15 (Xiaomi HyperOS 3) when the app goes to background.
  - TlsSecurityHelper.java: AGPL v3 (original)
      TLS 1.2+ enforcement helper for HTTPS connections to the Lichess
      Tablebase API on older Android versions (API 21-27).
  - RootDetector.java: AGPL v3 (original)
      Non-blocking root detection. The result is informational only —
      the app never refuses to run on a rooted device because it is an
      offline chess app with no sensitive data to protect. The check
      is reported to the user via the About dialog.

See the root-level LICENSE-AGPL v3, LICENSE-GPL v3, and NOTICE files
for full license texts and attribution details.
